排自學緊微積分<br />\n<br />\n如果自變數係任何正整數，例如f(2)=f'(2) limt h&infin;-&gt;0 ｛f(2-h)-f(2)｝/h = 0 咁derivative答案會係0<br />\n<br />\n但係如果自變數係x，例如f(x)=f'(x) limt h&infin;-&gt;0 ｛f(x-h)-f(x)｝/h = 1 咁derivative答案會係1<br />\n<br />\n但係如果個x係正整數呢？點解唔係同上邊個條式咁<br />\n｛<del>f(x</del>-h)-<del>f(x)</del>｝/h <br />\n=0/h 因h無限接近0<br />\n=0?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3iEEDxrhyE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx3iEEDxrhyE&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=37ab547b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3iEEDxrhyE</a><br />\n<br />\n5:20秒度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"如果任何function h-&gt;0,  f(x-h)-f(x)都等於0，中學學微分就唔駛咁辛苦，全部f&rsquo;(x)=0<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425ae09d4fb45e87b609f44f9830cf6e18dfad70","tid":2190430,"uid":205457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:57:13.000Z","msg":"其實微分就係搵切線嘅「斜率」，你用嘅first principle就係喺條線度搵兩點畫個直角三角形，然後高除底去計個斜率，只係個兩點相差接近0<br />\n<br />\n條片入面都有講，假如f(x) = constant，e.g. f(x)=5，咁個function 係圖入面就係一條水平線，一條水平線自然就冇「斜率」啦，所以D一個constant咪等於0 囉<br />\n<br />\n當你D  f(x)=x嘅時候，用簡單嘅斜率方程式都可以知道答案，y=mx+c ，斜率即m=1 ，所以f&rsquo;(x)=1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而f(x)=x^2嘅斜率，用first principle計完一輪，f&rsquo;(x)=2x，2x就係f(x)=x^2係任何一點嘅切線嘅斜率"},{"pid":"4bb11a890608b8fcb41735855b25ef5c9191d622","tid":2190430,"uid":200583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個睇唔明問乜<br />\ndifferentiation嘅對象嘅function variable點解會可以係正整數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129f138c2eb01e9101c8832270474002bc71e96f","tid":2190430,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bb11a890608b8fcb41735855b25ef5c9191d622","tid":2190430,"uid":200583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T19:0